### 🧪 Database & Entity Framework Core HTTP Test Client

# Konfigurasi Environment
@hostname = localhost
@port = 5000
@host = http://{{hostname}}:{{port}}

###
# 1. Ambil Semua Posts (Menggunakan LINQ + JOIN)
GET {{host}}/api/database/posts

###

# 2. Cari Post Menggunakan Filter Pencarian
GET {{host}}/api/database/posts?search=ASP.NET

###

# 3. Ambil Statistik Data (Aggregate Queries)
GET {{host}}/api/database/stats

###

# 4. Uji Coba Transaksi Sukses (Commit)
POST {{host}}/api/database/transaction-demo?triggerError=false

###

# 5. Uji Coba Transaksi Gagal (Rollback - Database tetap aman/bersih)
POST {{host}}/api/database/transaction-demo?triggerError=true
